---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — Patriot Directory"
  description="Terms of service for Patriot Directory. Read the terms governing use of our free business directory."
>
  <section class="bg-navy text-white py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-white/70 mt-2">Last updated: February 23, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-navy max-w-none">
      <h2 class="font-display text-navy">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>
        By accessing and using Patriot Directory ("the Site"), you accept and agree
        to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms,
        please do not use the Site.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-navy">Description of Service</h2>
      <p>
        Patriot Directory is a free online directory of American-owned businesses.
        We provide business listings, maps, and category browsing as a public
        service to help consumers discover and support American businesses.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-navy">Use of the Site</h2>
      <p>You agree to use the Site only for lawful purposes and in a manner that does not:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Infringe the rights of others</li>
        <li>Restrict or inhibit anyone else's use of the Site</li>
        <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the Site</li>
        <li>Use automated tools to scrape or harvest data from the Site</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-display text-navy">Business Listings</h2>
      <p>
        Business listings are curated by our team based on publicly available
        information. We make reasonable efforts to ensure accuracy but do not
        guarantee the completeness or accuracy of any listing information.
      </p>
      <p>
        Inclusion in the directory does not constitute an endorsement of any
        business. We are not responsible for the products, services, or practices
        of listed businesses.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you are a business owner and wish to update or remove your listing,
        please contact us at
        <a href="mailto:hello@patriotdirectory.com" class="text-crimson">hello@patriotdirectory.com</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-navy">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        The Site's design, layout, and original content are the property of
        Patriot Directory. Business information, logos, and images belong to their
        respective owners and are displayed for directory purposes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-navy">Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
      <p>
        The Site is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, either
        express or implied. We do not warrant that the Site will be uninterrupted,
        error-free, or free of viruses or other harmful components.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-navy">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the fullest extent permitted by law, Patriot Directory shall not be
        liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive
        damages arising from your use of the Site.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-navy">Links to Third Parties</h2>
      <p>
        The Site contains links to third-party websites (business websites,
        social media profiles, map services). We are not responsible for the
        content or practices of these external sites.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-navy">Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. Changes will be
        posted on this page. Your continued use of the Site after changes are
        posted constitutes acceptance of the modified Terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-navy">Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of South Carolina,
        United States, without regard to conflict of law principles.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-navy">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these Terms? Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:hello@patriotdirectory.com" class="text-crimson">hello@patriotdirectory.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
